title: President Donald J. Trump Is Unleashing America’s 5G Potential – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Infrastructure & Technology

Secure 5G networks will absolutely be a vital link to America’s prosperity and national security in the 21st century.
						President Donald J. Trump					FREEING UP RESOURCES: President Donald J. Trump is taking decisive action to release more spectrum for commercial use, strengthening the United States’ leadership in 5G communications.
